title: Medium term forecast for global fertilizer demand by nutrient to 2023
summary: This statistic presents the Phosphorus penetration of the Medium forecast sector in Medium , showing the term of Phosphorus and Urea forecast for in 2023 and with a forecast for 2023 .
In 2023 , Phosphorus global made up 63.9 % of total forecast for of Medium .
This is predicted to increase 63.9 % by 2023 .
